Lazer Guided Melodies, the first album by the British space rock group Spiritualized. The inaugural line up of the band consisted of Jason Pierce (vocals, guitars), Mark Refoy (guitars), Will Carruthers (bass), Jonny Mattock (drums) and Kate Radley (keyboards).
